extendedInfo.description: WP7 Pink is a free pink/black theme for GOSMS Pro inspired in the slick and mimalistic Windows Phone 7 interface.IMPORTANT: You need to install GOSMS Pro first, it's FREE, then this theme.Instructions:1. Download GOSMS Pro from the Android Market for free.2. Download WP7 theme from here.3. Go to GOSMS > Settings > Theme > WP7 Pink.4. Enjoy!Keywords: GO SMS, WP7, WP8 theme, Windows Phone 7 theme, Minimal, Minimalistic, Cute, Pink, Black.
